metadata.name: Deq
metadata.description:
Deq (Tattoo), which has the meaning and story of each line, and consists of lines in which people embroider their feelings on their body, was usually made by women throughout history, but rarely by men; It has become a symbol of pain, joy, hope, fertility and power.
